<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ko">
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <title>EMA521_07_IH_0005</title>

    <!-- 공통 js-->
    <script src="../../common_contents/common/js/app.js"></script>
    <script src="../../common_practice/common/js/solve_area_act.js"></script>

    <!-- 공통 css-->
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="./../../common_contents/common/css/app.css" />

    <!-- 개별 -->
    <!-- <script src="../../common_practice/js/ema521_01_02_ih.js"></script> -->
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="./../../common_practice/common/css/app.css" />
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="./../../common_practice/css/ema521_07.css" />
  </head>
  <body>
    <div id="app_wrap" class="ema521_07_ih_0005">
      <section class="title type2">
        <h2 data-head="5" lang="y">반올림하여 나타낸 수가 큰 것부터 차례대로 기호를 골라 보세요.</h2>
      </section>
      <section class="contents">
        <div class="question_box justify_center align_start">
          <div class="text_area">
            <ul>
              <li lang="y">㉠ 1.752를 반올림하여 소수 첫째 자리<br />까지 나타낸 수</li>
              <li lang="y">㉡ 1.783을 반올림하여 소수 둘째 자리<br />까지 나타낸 수</li>
              <li lang="y">㉢ 1.627을 반올림하여 일의 자리까지 나타낸 수</li>
            </ul>
          </div>
          <div class="dropdown_area">
            <p>(</p>
            <div class="dropdown_wrap">
              <select class="custom_dropdown" data-answer-single="㉢">
                <option value=""></option>
                <option value="㉠" lang="y">㉠</option>
                <option value="㉡" lang="y">㉡</option>
                <option value="㉢" lang="y">㉢</option>
              </select>
            </div>
            <span class="mr_8">,</span>
            <div class="dropdown_wrap">
              <select class="custom_dropdown" data-answer-single="㉠">
                <option value=""></option>
                <option value="㉠" lang="y">㉠</option>
                <option value="㉡" lang="y">㉡</option>
                <option value="㉢" lang="y">㉢</option>
              </select>
            </div>
            <span class="mr_8">,</span>
            <div class="dropdown_wrap">
              <select class="custom_dropdown" data-answer-single="㉡">
                <option value=""></option>
                <option value="㉠" lang="y">㉠</option>
                <option value="㉡" lang="y">㉡</option>
                <option value="㉢" lang="y">㉢</option>
              </select>
            </div>
            <p>)</p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="solve_area">
          <div class="inner_solve">
            <div class="flex">
              <strong class="tit_solve" lang="y">해설</strong>
              <div class="conts_solve">
                <p lang="y">㉠ 1.7<span class="text_bg_red">5</span>2를 반올림하여 소수 첫째 자리까지 나타내면 1.8입니다.</p>
                <p lang="y">㉡ 1.78<span class="text_bg_red">3</span>을 반올림하여 소수 둘째 자리까지 나타내면 1.78입니다.</p>
                <p lang="y">㉢ 1.<span class="text_bg_red">6</span>27을 반올림하여 일의 자리까지 나타내면 2입니다.</p>
                <p lang="y">따라서 2>1.8>1.78이므로 반올림하여 나타낸 수가 큰 것부터 차례대로 기호를 쓰면 ㉢, ㉠, ㉡입니다.</p>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="buttons_solve"></div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="btn_area">
          <button class="btnType key">입력타입토글</button>
          <button class="btnReset">리셋</button>
          <button class="btnCheck">확인</button>
        </div>
      </section>
    </div>
  </body>
</html>
